{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775856896911,"sessionID":"ses_286ae8badffeRPJF9Fd7bLAANm","part":{"id":"prt_d7951c33d001AD0EQafDx3hSB4","messageID":"msg_d7951a036001thKii4NwlhzxjP","sessionID":"ses_286ae8badffeRPJF9Fd7bLAANm","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-c85ef894e6724ec0a752f7441ddbd791","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/store` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Stage | ST-0 |\n12: \n13: ## Scope\n14: \n15: 定义会话存储的抽象接口和数据结构，包括:\n16: - `SessionStore` 接口定义\n17: - `Session` 数据结构\n18: - 存储操作方法签名\n19: \n20: ## Out of Scope\n21: \n22: - 具体存储实现 (Redis、Memory 等)\n23: - 存储连接池管理\n24: - 分布式锁实现\n25: \n26: ## Dependencies\n27: \n28: 无外部依赖。\n29: \n30: ## Deliverables\n31: \n32: | File | Description |\n33: |------|-------------|\n34: | `pkg/store/store.go` | SessionStore 接口定义 |\n35: | `pkg/store/session.go` | Session 数据结构 |\n36: | `pkg/store/doc.go` | 包文档 |\n37: \n38: ## Acceptance Criteria\n39: \n40: - [ ] 接口定义完整\n41: - [ ] Session 数据结构包含必要字段\n42: - [ ] 通过 `go vet` 和 `golangci-lint`\n43: \n44: ## References\n45: \n46: - 待补充\n\n(End of file - total 46 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/store` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\n定义会话存储的抽象接口和数据结构，包括:\n- `SessionStore` 接口定义\n- `Session` 数据结构\n- 存储操作方法签名\n\n## Out of Scope","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/spec.md","t