{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775856896913,"sessionID":"ses_286ae8badffeRPJF9Fd7bLAANm","part":{"id":"prt_d7951bf85001LVBdf3Du0gkddQ","messageID":"msg_d7951a036001thKii4NwlhzxjP","sessionID":"ses_286ae8badffeRPJF9Fd7bLAANm","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-f2ffb7da41a34202b6faf9031ecb60e2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 Proposal\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: 定义会话存储的抽象接口层，为 AgentCube 的会话管理提供统一的存储抽象。该接口设计遵循以下原则:\n6: \n7: 1. **接口抽象**: 定义标准 CRUD 操作接口，支持多种存储后端实现\n8: 2. **数据结构**: Session 结构包含会话标识、状态、生命周期等核心字段\n9: 3. **扩展性**: 接口设计支持未来扩展 (如批量操作、事务支持)\n10: \n11: ## Scope\n12: \n13: ### In Scope\n14: \n15: | Deliverable | Description |\n16: |-------------|-------------|\n17: | `pkg/store/store.go` | SessionStore 接口定义，包含 CRUD 方法签名 |\n18: | `pkg/store/session.go` | Session 数据结构，包含必要字段定义 |\n19: | `pkg/store/doc.go` | 包文档 |\n20: \n21: ### Out of Scope\n22: \n23: - 具体存储实现 (Redis、Memory、Etcd 等)\n24: - 存储连接池管理\n25: - 分布式锁实现\n26: - 缓存策略\n27: - 存储健康检查\n28: \n29: ## Impact Analysis\n30: \n31: ### Upstream Dependencies\n32: \n33: | Dependency | Impact |\n34: |------------|--------|\n35: | `time` | Session 生命周期时间字段 |\n36: | `context` | 操作上下文传递 |\n37: \n38: ### Downstream Consumers\n39: \n40: | Consumer | Usage |\n41: |----------|-------|\n42: | Session Manager | 使用 SessionStore 接口管理会话 |\n43: | Router | 通过 SessionStore 查询会话状态 |\n44: | Workload Manager | 创建/更新会话状态 |\n45: | 存储实现模块 | 实现 SessionStore 接口 |\n46: \n47: ### Breaking Change Considerations\n48: \n49: - **接口签名变更**: 新增/修改方法签名会影响所有实现\n50: - **Session 字段变更**: 添加/删除字段需同步所有消费者\n51: - **错误类型变更**: 返回错误类型变更需消费者适配\n52: \n53: ## Alternatives Considered\n54: \n55: ### Alternative 1: 直接使用 Redis Client\n56: \n57: **Approach**: 不定义抽象接口，直接在各模块使用 Redis 客户端。\n58: \n59: | Aspect | Evaluation |\n60: |--------|------------|\n61: | Pros | 简单直接，减少抽象层 |\n62: | Cons | 无法切换存储后端；测试困难；Redis 依赖渗透 |\n63: \n64: **Decision**: Rejected. 接口抽象支持多后端实现和测试 mock。\n65: \n66: ### Alternative 2: 使用第三方存储库\n67: \n68: **Approach**: 使用如 `gocache` 等第三方存储抽象库。\n69: \n70: | Aspect | Evaluation |\n71: |--------|------------|\n72: | Pros | 功能完善，社区支持 |\n73: | Cons | 过度依赖；接口可能不匹配 AgentCube 需求 |\n74: \n75: **Decision**: Rejected. AgentCube 需求简单，自定义接口更灵活。\n76: \n77: ## Risks\n78: \n79: | Risk | Mitigation |\n80: |------|------------|\n81: | 接口设计不完整 | 参考现有 Session Manager 使用场景 |\n82: | Session 字段遗漏 | 核对 Router/Workload Manager 需求 |\n83: \n84: ## Implementation Notes\n85: \n86: 1. 接口方法返回 error，支持自定义错误类型\n87: 2. Session 结构使用时间戳而非 Duration，便于存储\n88: 3. 使用 context.Context 支持操作超时和取消\n89: \n90: ## References\n91: \n92: - 待补充\n\n(End of file - total 92 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 Proposal\n\n## Purpose\n\n定义会话存储的抽象接口层，为 AgentCube 的会话管理提供统一的存储抽象。该接口设计遵循以下原则:\n\n1. **接口抽象**: 定义标准 CRUD 操作接口，支持多种存储后端实现\n2. **数据结构**: Session 结构包含会话标识、状态、生命周期等核心字段\n3. **扩展性**: 接口设计支持未来扩展 (如批量操作、事务支持)\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n| Deliverable | Description |\n|-------------|-------------|\n| `pkg/store/store.go` | SessionStore 接口定义，包含 CRUD 方法签名 |\n| `pkg/store/session.go` | Session 数据结构，包含必要字段定义 |\n| `pkg/store/doc.go` | 包文档 |\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775856896863,"end":1775856896911}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775856896914,"sessionID":"ses_286ae8badffeRPJF9Fd7bLAANm","part":{"id":"prt_d7951c6cd001QRUHLcRH1atmr2","messageID":"msg_d7951a036001thKii4NwlhzxjP","sessionID":"ses_286ae8badffeRPJF9Fd7bLAANm","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-fffeebdc861c429b9d7e5dd3b8a63f78","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/store` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Stage | ST-1 |\n12: \n13: 定义会话存储的抽象接口层，为 Session Manager 提供统一的存储操作接口。\n14: \n15: ## Design\n16: \n17: ### Architecture\n18: \n19: 接口设计遵循 Go 接口惯例:\n20: - 方法签名简洁，返回 error\n21: - 使用 context.Context 支持超时/取消\n22: - Session 结构可序列化，支持多种存储后端\n23: \n24: ### Dependencies\n25: \n26: | Package | Purpose |\n27: |---------|---------|\n28: | `context` | 操作上下文 |\n29: | `time` | 时间字段 |\n30: \n31: ## Data Structures\n32: \n33: ### SessionStore Interface\n34: \n35: ```go\n36: type SessionStore interface {\n37:     Create(ctx context.Context, session *Session) error\n38:     Get(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*Session, error)\n39:     Update(ctx context.Context, session *Session) error\n40:     Delete(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n41:     List(ctx context.Context, filter *SessionFilter) ([]*Session, error)\n42: }\n43: ```\n44: \n45: ### Session\n46: \n47: ```go\n48: type Session struct {\n49:     ID           string    `json:\"id\"`\n50:     SandboxID    string    `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n51:     Namespace    string    `json:\"namespace\"`\n52:     Name         string    `json:\"name\"`\n53:     Status       string    `json:\"status\"`\n54:     CreatedAt    time.Time `json:\"createdAt\"`\n55:     UpdatedAt    time.Time `json:\"updatedAt\"`\n56:     ExpiresAt    time.Time `json:\"expiresAt\"`\n57:     LastActiveAt time.Time `json:\"lastActiveAt\"`\n58: }\n59: ```\n60: \n61: ### SessionFilter\n62: \n63: ```go\n64: type SessionFilter struct {\n65:     Namespace string\n66:     Status    string\n67:     Name      string\n68: }\n69: ```\n70: \n71: ## API Contracts\n72: \n73: ### Create\n74: \n75: ```go\n76: func Create(ctx context.Context, session *Session) error\n77: ```\n78: - Input: Session pointer with required fields populated\n79: - Output: error on failure, nil on success\n80: \n81: ### Get\n82: \n83: ```go\n84: func Get(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*Session, error)\n85: ```\n86: - Input: sessionID string\n87: - Output: Session pointer, error (including NotFound error)\n88: \n89: ### Update\n90: \n91: ```go\n92: func Update(ctx context.Context, session *Session) error\n93: ```\n94: - Input: Session pointer with updated fields\n95: - Output: error on failure, nil on success\n96: \n97: ### Delete\n98: \n99: ```go\n100: func Delete(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n101: ```\n102: - Input: sessionID string\n103: - Output: error on failure, nil on success\n104: \n105: ### List\n106: \n107: ```go\n108: func List(ctx context.Context, filter *SessionFilter) ([]*Session, error)\n109: ```\n110: - Input: optional SessionFilter\n111: - Output: slice of Session pointers, error\n112: \n113: ## Error Handling\n114: \n115: 建议定义自定义错误类型:\n116: - `SessionNotFoundError` - 会话不存在\n117: - `SessionAlreadyExistsError` - 会话已存在\n118: - `SessionStoreError` - 存储操作失败\n119: \n120: ## Testing Strategy\n121: \n122: ### Unit Tests\n123: \n124: | Test Category | Coverage |\n125: |---------------|----------|\n126: | Session 结构序列化 | JSON 序列化/反序列化正确 |\n127: | SessionFilter 过滤 | 过滤字段正确匹配 |\n128: \n129: ### Integration Tests\n130: \n131: - Mock 实现测试接口契约\n132: - 真实存储实现验证 (后续实现模块)\n133: \n134: ### Test Utilities\n135: \n136: ```go\n137: type MockSessionStore struct {\n138:     sessions map[string]*Session\n139:     // 实现所有接口方法\n140: }\n141: ```\n142: \n143: ## File Structure\n144: \n145: ```\n146: pkg/store/\n147:   store.go     — SessionStore 接口定义\n148:   session.go   — Session、SessionFilter 数据结构\n149:   doc.go       — 包文档\n150: ```\n151: \n152: ## Open Questions\n153: \n154: - 是否需要支持批量操作 (BatchCreate/BatchDelete)?\n155: - 是否需要支持事务操作?\n156: - SessionFilter 是否需要更多过滤字段?\n157: \n158: ## References\n159: \n160: - 待补充\n\n(End of file - total 160 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/store` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n定义会话存储的抽象接口层，为 Session Manager 提供统一的存储操作接口。\n\n## Design\n\n### Architecture\n\n接口设计遵循 Go 接口惯例:\n- 方法签名简洁，返回 error","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/design.md","time":{"start":1775856896871,"end":1775856896913}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775856896917,"sessionID":"ses_286ae8badffeRPJF9Fd7bLAANm","part":{"id":"prt_d7951cb48001NuyXh4od5BuZH7","messageID":"msg_d7951a036001thKii4NwlhzxjP","sessionID":"ses_286ae8badffeRPJF9Fd7bLAANm","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-c52475cc7ca94c3dbbcbdb2c2d5d555e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 Tasks\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/store` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Design | [Stage ST-0] |\n12: \n13: ---\n14: \n15: ## Task Checklist\n16: \n17: ### Phase 1: Project Setup\n18: \n19: - [ ] **T1.1** Create directory structure `pkg/store/`\n20: - [ ] **T1.2** Verify Go module exists and add dependencies if needed\n21: \n22: ### Phase 2: Core Type Definitions\n23: \n24: - [ ] **T2.1** Create `pkg/store/doc.go`\n25:   - Add package documentation\n26:   - Describe store module purpose\n27: \n28: - [ ] **T2.2** Create `pkg/store/session.go`\n29:   - Define `Session` struct with fields:\n30:     - `ID string`\n31:     - `SandboxID string`\n32:     - `Namespace string`\n33:     - `Name string`\n34:     - `Status string`\n35:     - `CreatedAt time.Time`\n36:     - `UpdatedAt time.Time`\n37:     - `ExpiresAt time.Time`\n38:     - `LastActiveAt time.Time`\n39:   - Add JSON tags for serialization\n40:   - Verify: `go build ./pkg/store/`\n41: \n42: - [ ] **T2.3** Create `pkg/store/store.go`\n43:   - Define `SessionStore` interface with methods:\n44:     - `Create(ctx, session) error`\n45:     - `Get(ctx, sessionID) (*Session, error)`\n46:     - `Update(ctx, session) error`\n47:     - `Delete(ctx, sessionID) error`\n48:     - `List(ctx, filter) ([]*Session, error)`\n49:   - Define `SessionFilter` struct for list filtering\n50:   - Verify: `go build ./pkg/store/`\n51: \n52: ### Phase 3: Error Types (Optional)\n53: \n54: - [ ] **T3.1** Define custom error types in `pkg/store/errors.go`\n55:   - `SessionNotFoundError`\n56:   - `SessionAlreadyExistsError`\n57:   - `SessionStoreError`\n58:   - Verify: `go build ./pkg/store/`\n59: \n60: ### Phase 4: Unit Tests\n61: \n62: - [ ] **T4.1** Create `pkg/store/session_test.go`\n63:   - Test Session struct JSON serialization/deserialization\n64:   - Test SessionFilter with various filter combinations\n65:   - Verify: `go test ./pkg/store/... -v`\n66: \n67: ### Phase 5: Validation & Quality\n68: \n69: - [ ] **T5.1** Run `go vet ./pkg/store/...`\n70:   - Fix any issues reported\n71: \n72: - [ ] **T5.2** Run `golangci-lint run ./pkg/store/...`\n73:   - Fix any linting issues\n74: \n75: - [ ] **T5.3** Verify JSON tags use camelCase\n76:   - Check: `sandboxId`, `createdAt`, `updatedAt`, `expiresAt`, `lastActiveAt`\n77: \n78: ---\n79: \n80: ## Task Dependencies\n81: \n82: ```\n83: T1.1 → T1.2 → T2.1 → T2.2 → T2.3 → T3.1 → T4.1 → T5.1 → T5.2 → T5.3\n84: ```\n85: \n86: ---\n87: \n88: ## Verification Commands\n89: \n90: | Task | Verification Command |\n91: |------|----------------------|\n92: | T1.2 | `go mod tidy && go mod verify` |\n93: | T2.1-T2.3 | `go build ./pkg/store/...` |\n94: | T3.1 | `go build ./pkg/store/...` |\n95: | T4.1 | `go test ./pkg/store/... -v -cover` |\n96: | T5.1 | `go vet ./pkg/store/...` |\n97: | T5.2 | `golangci-lint run ./pkg/store/...` |\n98: \n99: ---\n100: \n101: ## Acceptance Criteria\n102: \n103: - [ ] SessionStore 接口定义完整\n104: - [ ] Session 数据结构包含必要字段\n105: - [ ] SessionFilter 支持基本过滤\n106: - [ ] Pass `go vet` with zero issues\n107: - [ ] Pass `golangci-lint` with zero issues\n108: - [ ] JSON tags 使用 camelCase\n109: - [ ] Unit tests pass\n110: \n111: ---\n112: \n113: ## Notes\n114: \n115: - 仅定义接口，不实现具体存储逻辑\n116: - 具体实现由后续 AR 提供 (如 Redis 实现)\n117: - 接口设计参考 Session Manager 使用场景\n118: \n119: ---\n120: \n121: ## Implementation Timeline\n122: \n123: | Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n124: |-------|-------|--------|------------|\n125: | Phase 1: Project Setup | T1.1-T1.2 | Not Started | 0% |\n126: | Phase 2: Core Type Definitions | T2.1-T2.3 | Not Started | 0% |\n127: | Phase 3: Error Types | T3.1 | Not Started | 0% |\n128: | Phase 4: Unit Tests | T4.1 | Not Started | 0% |\n129: | Phase 5: Validation | T5.1-T5.3 | Not Started | 0% |\n130: \n131: **Total Progress: 0% Complete**\n\n(End of file - total 131 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/store` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Design | [Stage ST-0] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Project Setup\n\n- [ ] **T1.1** Create directory structure `pkg/store/`\n- [ ] **T1.2** Verify Go module exists and add dependencies if needed","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775856896873,"end":1775856896915}}}}
