{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775857026769,"sessionID":"ses_286ae8badffeRPJF9Fd7bLAANm","part":{"id":"prt_d795271e3001aKISkTyBHIhoQW","messageID":"msg_d79521d3b001aDJTUpFmnxXy7b","sessionID":"ses_286ae8badffeRPJF9Fd7bLAANm","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-c1535f01815249f3b950c80a7bbbd191","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-013/proposal.md","content":"# AR-013 — Redis 存储实现 Proposal\n\n## Purpose\n\n实现 Redis 存储后端，为 AgentCube 的会话管理提供高性能、持久化的存储能力。该实现基于 AR-012 定义的 SessionStore 接口，遵循以下原则:\n\n1. **接口实现**: 实现 SessionStore 接口的所有方法\n2. **Redis 最佳实践**: 使用连接池、Pipeline 优化、合理的数据结构\n3. **可靠性**: 支持重试、超时控制、错误处理\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n| Deliverable | Description |\n|-------------|-------------|\n| `pkg/store/redis.go` | RedisSessionStore 实现 SessionStore 接口 |\n| `pkg/store/redis_config.go` | Redis 配置结构和默认值 |\n| `pkg/store/redis_test.go` | Redis 存储单元测试 |\n\n### Out of Scope\n\n- Redis 集群部署\n- 分布式锁实现\n- 缓存预热策略\n- 数据迁移工具\n- Redis Sentinel/Cluster 支持\n\n## Impact Analysis\n\n### Upstream Dependencies\n\n| Dependency | Impact |\n|------------|--------|\n| `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9` | Redis 客户端库 |\n| AR-012 SessionStore 接口 | 需实现所有方法 |\n| `context` | 操作上下文传递 |\n| `encoding/json` | Session 序列化 |\n\n### Downstream Consumers\n\n| Consumer | Usage |\n|----------|-------|\n| Session Manager | 通过 SessionStore 接口使用 Redis 存储 |\n| Router | 查询会话状态 |\n| Workload Manager | 创建/更新会话 |\n\n### Breaking Change Considerations\n\n- **配置变更**: 新增 Redis 配置项，需同步配置文件\n- **依赖引入**: 新增 go-redis 依赖\n- **部署变更**: 需部署 Redis 实例\n\n## Alternatives Considered\n\n### Alternative 1: 使用内存存储\n\n**Approach**: 使用 sync.Map 或 map 实现内存存储。\n\n| Aspect | Evaluation |\n|--------|------------|\n| Pros | 简单，无需外部依赖 |\n| Cons | 数据不持久化，重启丢失；不支持分布式 |\n\n**Decision**: Rejected. 生产环境需要持久化和分布式支持。\n\n### Alternative 2: 使用 Etcd 存储\n\n**Approach**: 使用 Etcd 作为存储后端。\n\n| Aspect | Evaluation |\n|--------|------------|\n| Pros | 强一致性，支持 watch |\n| Cons | 性能不如 Redis；运维复杂度高 |\n\n**Decision**: Rejected. 会话存储对性能要求高于一致性。\n\n## Risks\n\n| Risk | Mitigation |\n|------|------------|\n| Redis 连接失败 | 实现重试机制和连接池 |\n| 数据序列化失败 | 严格的单元测试覆盖 |\n| 性能不达标 | Pipeline 批量操作优化 |\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n1. 使用 go-redis v9 作为 Redis 客户端\n2. Session 存储使用 Hash 结构，key 格式: `session:{sessionID}`\n3. 支持过期时间自动清理\n4. 配置支持连接池、超时、重试参数\n\n## References\n\n- AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义\n- Redis 官方文档: https://redis.io/docs/\n- go-redis 文档: https://redis.uptrace.dev/"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-013/proposal.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-013/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775857026720,"end":1775857026768}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775857026771,"sessionID":"ses_286ae8badffeRPJF9Fd7bLAANm","part":{"id":"prt_d795292a80011wWZevTnctXz71","messageID":"msg_d79521d3b001aDJTUpFmnxXy7b","sessionID":"ses_286ae8badffeRPJF9Fd7bLAANm","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-026df856649542dcb2b1e9e26d124e69","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-013/spec.md","content":"# AR-013 — Redis 存储实现\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-013 — Redis 存储实现 |\n| Module | `pkg/store` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\n实现 Redis 存储后端，包括:\n- `RedisSessionStore` 结构实现 SessionStore 接口\n- Redis 配置管理\n- Session 序列化/反序列化\n- 错误处理\n\n## Out of Scope\n\n- Redis 集群支持\n- 分布式锁\n- 缓存预热\n- 数据迁移\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Dependency | Version | Purpose |\n|------------|---------|---------|\n| AR-012 | - | SessionStore 接口定义 |\n| go-redis/v9 | v9.x | Redis 客户端 |\n\n## Deliverables\n\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `pkg/store/redis.go` | RedisSessionStore 实现 |\n| `pkg/store/redis_config.go` | Redis 配置结构 |\n| `pkg/store/redis_test.go` | 单元测试 |\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] 实现完整的 SessionStore 接口\n- [ ] 支持配置化连接参数\n- [ ] 处理所有错误情况\n- [ ] 通过 `go vet` 和 `golangci-lint`\n- [ ] 单元测试覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n\n## References\n\n- AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-013/spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-013/spec.md","time":{"start":1775857026730,"end":1775857026770}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775857026773,"sessionID":"ses_286ae8badffeRPJF9Fd7bLAANm","part":{"id":"prt_d79533017001MWB2aEo4dcUiqQ","messageID":"msg_d79521d3b001aDJTUpFmnxXy7b","sessionID":"ses_286ae8badffeRPJF9Fd7bLAANm","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-6bcd8f2f94a64c7ebe4aebb0ab3a040b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-013/design.md","content":"# AR-013 — Redis 存储实现 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-013 — Redis 存储实现 |\n| Module | `pkg/store` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n实现 Redis 存储后端，提供高性能的会话持久化能力。\n\n## Design\n\n### Architecture\n\n```\n┌─────────────────┐\n│ Session Manager │\n└────────┬────────┘\n         │\n         v\n┌─────────────────┐\n│ SessionStore    │  (Interface - AR-012)\n└────────┬────────┘\n         │\n         v\n┌─────────────────┐\n│RedisSessionStore│  (Implementation - AR-013)\n└────────┬────────┘\n         │\n         v\n┌─────────────────┐\n│  go-redis/v9    │\n└────────┬────────┘\n         │\n         v\n┌─────────────────┐\n│     Redis       │\n└─────────────────┘\n```\n\n### Dependencies\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|\n| `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9` | Redis 客户端 |\n| `context` | 操作上下文 |\n| `encoding/json` | Session 序列化 |\n| `time` | 时间处理 |\n\n## Data Structures\n\n### RedisConfig\n\n```go\ntype RedisConfig struct {\n    Addr         string        // Redis 地址\n    Password     string        // 密码\n    DB           int           // 数据库\n    PoolSize     int           // 连接池大小\n    MinIdleConns int           // 最小空闲连接\n    MaxRetries   int           // 最大重试次数\n    DialTimeout  time.Duration // 连接超时\n    ReadTimeout  time.Duration // 读超时\n    WriteTimeout time.Duration // 写超时\n}\n```\n\n### RedisSessionStore\n\n```go\ntype RedisSessionStore struct {\n    client *redis.Client\n    config *RedisConfig\n}\n```\n\n## API Contracts\n\n### Constructor\n\n```go\nfunc NewRedisSessionStore(cfg *RedisConfig) (*RedisSessionStore, error)\n```\n- Input: RedisConfig 指针\n- Output: RedisSessionStore 实例，error\n\n### SessionStore Interface Methods\n\n#### Create\n\n```go\nfunc (s *RedisSessionStore) Create(ctx context.Context, session *Session) error\n```\n- Key: `session:{sessionID}`\n- 使用 HSET 存储 Session 字段\n- 设置过期时间: EXPIREAT session.ExpiresAt\n\n#### Get\n\n```go\nfunc (s *RedisSessionStore) Get(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*Session, error)\n```\n- Key: `session:{sessionID}`\n- 使用 HGETALL 获取所有字段\n- 返回 SessionNotFoundError 如果不存在\n\n#### Update\n\n```go\nfunc (s *RedisSessionStore) Update(ctx context.Context, session *Session) error\n```\n- Key: `session:{sessionID}`\n- 使用 HSET 更新字段\n- 更新 UpdatedAt 时间戳\n\n#### Delete\n\n```go\nfunc (s *RedisSessionStore) Delete(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n```\n- Key: `session:{sessionID}`\n- 使用 DEL 删除 key\n\n#### List\n\n```go\nfunc (s *RedisSessionStore) List(ctx context.Context, filter *SessionFilter) ([]*Session, error)\n```\n- 使用 SCAN 遍历 `session:*` keys\n- 根据 filter 过滤结果\n- 注意: 大量数据时需要分页\n\n## Error Handling\n\n### Custom Errors\n\n```go\nvar (\n    ErrRedisNotConnected = errors.New(\"redis: not connected\")\n    ErrSessionNotFound   = errors.New(\"session: not found\")\n    ErrInvalidConfig     = errors.New(\"redis: invalid config\")\n)\n```\n\n### Error Wrapping\n\n```go\nif err := s.client.Get(ctx, key).Err(); err == redis.Nil {\n    return nil, fmt.Errorf(\"get session %s: %w\", sessionID, ErrSessionNotFound)\n}\n```\n\n## Redis Key Design\n\n| Key Pattern | Type | TTL | Description |\n|-------------|------|-----|-------------|\n| `session:{id}` | Hash | ExpiresAt - now | Session 数据 |\n\n### Session Hash Fields\n\n```\nsession:abc123\n  id:           \"abc123\"\n  sandboxId:    \"sb-456\"\n  namespace:    \"default\"\n  name:         \"session-name\"\n  status:       \"active\"\n  createdAt:    \"2024-01-01T00:00:00Z\"\n  updatedAt:    \"2024-01-01T01:00:00Z\"\n  expiresAt:    \"2024-01-02T00:00:00Z\"\n  lastActiveAt: \"2024-01-01T01:30:00Z\"\n```\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n| Test Category | Coverage |\n|---------------|----------|\n| Create | 创建 session 并验证存储 |\n| Get | 获取存在的 session |\n| Get (not found) | 获取不存在的 session |\n| Update | 更新 session 字段 |\n| Delete | 删除 session |\n| List (no filter) | 列出所有 session |\n| List (with filter) | 按 namespace/status 过滤 |\n| TTL 处理 | 验证过期时间设置 |\n| 错误处理 | 连接失败、序列化失败 |\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n```go\nfunc TestRedisSessionStore_Integration(t *testing.T) {\n    // 使用 miniredis 或真实 Redis\n    // 验证端到端操作\n}\n```\n\n### Test Utilities\n\n```go\nfunc setupTestRedis(t *testing.T) *RedisSessionStore {\n    // 使用 miniredis 创建测试实例\n    // 或连接到 test Redis\n}\n```\n\n## File Structure\n\n```\npkg/store/\n  redis.go        — RedisSessionStore 实现\n  redis_config.go — RedisConfig 配置\n  redis_test.go   — 单元测试\n```\n\n## Performance Considerations\n\n1. **连接池**: 配置合理的 PoolSize 和 MinIdleConns\n2. **Pipeline**: 批量操作时使用 Pipeline 减少 RTT\n3. **序列化**: 使用 JSON 序列化，考虑 msgpack 优化\n4. **过期清理**: 使用 Redis TTL 自动清理过期 session\n\n## Configuration\n\n### Default RedisConfig\n\n```go\nvar DefaultRedisConfig = &RedisConfig{\n    Addr:         \"localhost:6379\",\n    Password:     \"\",\n    DB:           0,\n    PoolSize:     10,\n    MinIdleConns: 5,\n    MaxRetries:   3,\n    DialTimeout:  5 * time.Second,\n    ReadTimeout:  3 * time.Second,\n    WriteTimeout: 3 * time.Second,\n}\n```\n\n### Environment Variables\n\n| Variable | Config Field |\n|----------|--------------|\n| REDIS_ADDR | Addr |\n| REDIS_PASSWORD | Password |\n| REDIS_DB | DB |\n| REDIS_POOL_SIZE | PoolSize |\n\n## Open Questions\n\n- 是否需要支持 Redis Cluster?\n- 是否需要实现连接健康检查?\n- List 操作是否需要分页支持?\n- 是否需要实现批量操作 (Pipeline)?\n\n## References\n\n- AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义\n- Redis 官方文档: https://redis.io/docs/\n- go-redis 文档: https://redis.uptrace.dev/"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-013/design.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-013/design.md","time":{"start":1775857026751,"end":1775857026771}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775857026776,"sessionID":"ses_286ae8badffeRPJF9Fd7bLAANm","part":{"id":"prt_d7953c676001GMI23dIq51x1NK","messageID":"msg_d79521d3b001aDJTUpFmnxXy7b","sessionID":"ses_286ae8badffeRPJF9Fd7bLAANm","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-885ee0058fd842a999d96d0835914222","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-013/tasks.md","content":"# AR-013 — Redis 存储实现 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-013 — Redis 存储实现 |\n| Module | `pkg/store` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Design | [Stage ST-0] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Dependencies Setup\n\n- [ ] **T1.1** Add go-redis dependency\n  - Run: `go get github.com/redis/go-redis/v9`\n  - Update `go.mod` and `go.sum`\n\n- [ ] **T1.2** Verify AR-012 interface exists\n  - Check: `pkg/store/store.go` has SessionStore interface\n  - Check: `pkg/store/session.go` has Session struct\n  - If not exists, wait for AR-012 completion\n\n### Phase 2: Configuration\n\n- [ ] **T2.1** Create `pkg/store/redis_config.go`\n  - Define `RedisConfig` struct with fields:\n    - `Addr string`\n    - `Password string`\n    - `DB int`\n    - `PoolSize int`\n    - `MinIdleConns int`\n    - `MaxRetries int`\n    - `DialTimeout time.Duration`\n    - `ReadTimeout time.Duration`\n    - `WriteTimeout time.Duration`\n  - Define `DefaultRedisConfig` variable\n  - Add `Validate()` method\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/store/`\n\n### Phase 3: Redis Client Wrapper\n\n- [ ] **T3.1** Create `pkg/store/redis.go`\n  - Define `RedisSessionStore` struct\n  - Add client and config fields\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/store/`\n\n- [ ] **T3.2** Implement constructor\n  - Implement `NewRedisSessionStore(cfg *RedisConfig) (*RedisSessionStore, error)`\n  - Validate config\n  - Create redis.Client instance\n  - Test connection with Ping\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/store/`\n\n### Phase 4: SessionStore Interface Implementation\n\n- [ ] **T4.1** Implement `Create(ctx, session) error`\n  - Build key: `session:{session.ID}`\n  - Use HSET to store session fields\n  - Set expiration with EXPIREAT\n  - Handle errors (connection, serialization)\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/store/`\n\n- [ ] **T4.2** Implement `Get(ctx, sessionID) (*Session, error)`\n  - Build key: `session:{sessionID}`\n  - Use HGETALL to retrieve fields\n  - Return ErrSessionNotFound if not exists\n  - Deserialize to Session struct\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/store/`\n\n- [ ] **T4.3** Implement `Update(ctx, session) error`\n  - Build key: `session:{session.ID}`\n  - Update UpdatedAt timestamp\n  - Use HSET to update fields\n  - Handle errors\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/store/`\n\n- [ ] **T4.4** Implement `Delete(ctx, sessionID) error`\n  - Build key: `session:{sessionID}`\n  - Use DEL to remove key\n  - Handle errors\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/store/`\n\n- [ ] **T4.5** Implement `List(ctx, filter) ([]*Session, error)`\n  - Use SCAN to iterate `session:*` keys\n  - Filter by namespace, status, name\n  - Deserialize each session\n  - Return slice of sessions\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/store/`\n\n### Phase 5: Error Types\n\n- [ ] **T5.1** Define error types in `pkg/store/redis.go`\n  - `ErrRedisNotConnected`\n  - `ErrSessionNotFound`\n  - `ErrInvalidConfig`\n  - Wrap errors with context\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/store/`\n\n### Phase 6: Unit Tests\n\n- [ ] **T6.1** Create `pkg/store/redis_test.go`\n  - Setup test environment (miniredis or real redis)\n  - Test `NewRedisSessionStore` constructor\n\n- [ ] **T6.2** Test Create operation\n  - Create session successfully\n  - Verify session stored in Redis\n  - Test TTL expiration\n\n- [ ] **T6.3** Test Get operation\n  - Get existing session\n  - Get non-existing session (expect ErrSessionNotFound)\n  - Test deserialization\n\n- [ ] **T6.4** Test Update operation\n  - Update session fields\n  - Verify UpdatedAt updated\n  - Test error cases\n\n- [ ] **T6.5** Test Delete operation\n  - Delete existing session\n  - Delete non-existing session\n  - Verify: `go test ./pkg/store/... -v -cover`\n\n- [ ] **T6.6** Test List operation\n  - List all sessions\n  - List with namespace filter\n  - List with status filter\n  - Verify: `go test ./pkg/store/... -v -cover`\n\n- [ ] **T6.7** Test error handling\n  - Connection failure\n  - Serialization errors\n  - Invalid config\n\n- [ ] **T6.8** Verify test coverage\n  - Run: `go test ./pkg/store/... -cover`\n  - Ensure coverage ≥ 80%\n\n### Phase 7: Validation & Quality\n\n- [ ] **T7.1** Run `go vet ./pkg/store/...`\n  - Fix any issues reported\n\n- [ ] **T7.2** Run `golangci-lint run ./pkg/store/...`\n  - Fix any linting issues\n\n- [ ] **T7.3** Run `go mod tidy`\n  - Clean up dependencies\n\n- [ ] **T7.4** Verify build\n  - Run: `go build ./pkg/store/...`\n  - Ensure no build errors\n\n---\n\n## Task Dependencies\n\n```\nT1.1 → T1.2 → T2.1 → T3.1 → T3.2 → T4.1 → T4.2 → T4.3 → T4.4 → T4.5\n                                                      ↓\n                                                    T5.1\n                                                      ↓\nT6.1 → T6.2 → T6.3 → T6.4 → T6.5 → T6.6 → T6.7 → T6.8\n                                                      ↓\n                                        T7.1 → T7.2 → T7.3 → T7.4\n```\n\n---\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n| Task | Verification Command |\n|------|----------------------|\n| T1.1 | `go mod tidy && go mod verify` |\n| T1.2 | `ls pkg/store/store.go pkg/store/session.go` |\n| T2.1-T3.2 | `go build ./pkg/store/...` |\n| T4.1-T4.5 | `go build ./pkg/store/...` |\n| T5.1 | `go build ./pkg/store/...` |\n| T6.1-T6.8 | `go test ./pkg/store/... -v -cover` |\n| T7.1 | `go vet ./pkg/store/...` |\n| T7.2 | `golangci-lint run ./pkg/store/...` |\n| T7.3 | `go mod tidy` |\n| T7.4 | `go build ./pkg/store/...` |\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] 实现 SessionStore 接口所有方法\n- [ ] 支持配置化连接参数\n- [ ] 错误处理完善\n- [ ] Pass `go vet` with zero issues\n- [ ] Pass `golangci-lint` with zero issues\n- [ ] Unit tests pass\n- [ ] Test coverage ≥ 80%\n- [ ] Redis key 设计合理\n- [ ] 支持 TTL 自动过期\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n\n- 依赖 AR-012 完成后才能实现\n- 使用 miniredis 进行单元测试，避免依赖真实 Redis\n- List 操作使用 SCAN 而非 KEYS，避免阻塞\n- 后续可扩展: Pipeline 优化、批量操作\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Timeline\n\n| Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n|-------|-------|--------|------------|\n| Phase 1: Dependencies | T1.1-T1.2 | Not Started | 0% |\n| Phase 2: Configuration | T2.1 | Not Started | 0% |\n| Phase 3: Client Wrapper | T3.1-T3.2 | Not Started | 0% |\n| Phase 4: Interface Impl | T4.1-T4.5 | Not Started | 0% |\n| Phase 5: Error Types | T5.1 | Not Started | 0% |\n| Phase 6: Unit Tests | T6.1-T6.8 | Not Started | 0% |\n| Phase 7: Validation | T7.1-T7.4 | Not Started | 0% |\n\n**Total Progress: 0% Complete**"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-013/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-013/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775857026758,"end":1775857026773}}}}
